text.section:
The Department shall:
advise the Board in connection with each engineering question or matter concerning construction of a State correctional facility;
supervise each engineering question or matter concerning the design or construction of a State correctional facility;
subject to subsection (b) of this section, approve each architectural and engineering design and service in connection with the construction of a State correctional facility; and
examine and approve or disapprove each design, plan, and specification prepared in connection with the preparation or execution of a contract for construction of a State correctional facility.
